1. BigVGAN: scratch (clean-room) reimplementation policy
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
The NVIDIA BigVGAN reference implementation is distributed under the
NVIDIA Source Code License-NC (non-commercial), which is incompatible with
Vokra's Apache 2.0 licensing. Vokra therefore does not use, port, or derive
code from the NVIDIA reference implementation. The BigVGAN-compatible
vocoder operator in Vokra will be reimplemented from scratch based on the
published paper only.

Timing note: this is a forward-looking policy statement. The BigVGAN
operator is not implemented in the current v0.1 spike (milestone M0); it is
planned for a future release, scheduled together with the models that
require it (see docs/milestones.md §1.3).

